  "title": "Azure Purview",
  "contentHtml": "In this episode Michael, Gladys and Mark talk with guests \n               Gopal Shankar (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/gopalshankar/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>) \n               and \n               Arvind Chandaka (<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/arvindchandaka/'><i class=\"fa-brands fa-linkedin\"></i></a>) \n               from the Azure Purview and Azure Information Protection team about a new governance product, Azure Purview. &nbsp;\n\n               <br>\n               We also discuss Azure Security news for the following: Azure Monitor, Storage, cryptography, Zero Trust, Incident Response, Azure Information Protection, Ransomware and more. \n      \n               <br><br>\n               <iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://player.rss.com/azsecpodcast/203354?theme=light\" class=\"podcast-player\" title=\"rss embed thingy\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><a href=\"https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/248603/\">TTTTTT | RSS.com Podcasting</a></iframe>\n\n               <h5>Links</h5> \n               <ul>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://rss.com/podcasts/azsecpodcast/203354/'>Transcript <i class=\"fa-solid fa-pencil\"></i></a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/azure-monitor/logs/customer-managed-keys?tabs=portal'>Azure Monitor customer-managed key</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/public-preview-stateful-and-1minute-frequency-log-alerts-in-azure-monitor/'>Public preview: Stateful and 1-minute frequency log alerts in Azure Monitor</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://cloudjourney.medium.com/azure-monitor-private-link-a8a4544facaf'>Azure Monitor Private Link</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/prevent-shared-key-authorization-for-an-azure-storage-account/'>Prevent Shared Key authorization for an Azure Storage account</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://michaelhowardsecure.blog/2021/05/09/the-best-security-advice-i-can-give/'>'The Best Security Advice I Can Give…'</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://michaelhowardsecure.blog/2021/05/08/please-be-pedantic-when-talking-about-cryptography/'>'Please be pedantic when talking about cryptography'</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://michaelhowardsecure.blog/2021/05/07/revisiting-some-thoughts-from-almost-20-years-ago/'>Revisiting some thoughts from almost 20 years ago</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security/compass/incident-response-playbooks'>Incident response playbooks</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security/compass/human-operated-ransomware'>Human operated ransomware</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://publications.opengroup.org/security-library/w210'>Zero Trust Core Principles</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=53018'>Microsoft Azure Information Protection</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/information-protection/rms-client/unifiedlabelingclient-version-release-history'>Azure Information Protection unified labeling client</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/updates/azure-storage-abac-preview/'>Azure Storage — Attribute-based Access Control (ABAC) now available for preview</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CwWYer1TmbY'>John Savill: New Attribute-Based Access Control for Blob</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/reports-monitoring/concept-all-sign-ins'>Sign-ins logs in Azure Active Directory - preview</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/purview/overview'>What is Azure Purview?</a></li>\n                  <li><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\" href='https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/purview/'>Azure Purview documentation</a></li>\n               </ul>"
